examples.description: Convergence analysis for two heuristic methods: an evolutionary algorithm and a harmony search algorithm for a 1000 Gbps demand between Kołobrzeg and Rzeszów using 36 shortest paths. The curve is the average of 20 individual runs.

Analysis with confidence intervals for two heuristic methods: an evolutionary algorithm and a harmony search algorithm and also MIP for reference (language: AMPL, solver: CPLEX). Done for a 1000 Gbps demand between Kołobrzeg and Rzeszów using 36 shortest paths. Summarizes 20 individual runs.
